I present to you, surf_happyhands5

Tier 3 | Linear| 2 (3) Bonuses

This is the 5th map in the series with the same vibe (kind of) from the first 4 others. As someone has said: "It's a happyhands map but on crack" - Granis.

It has been tested with default velocity (and is made for such) with 150/300 airaccelerate.

Also a big thanks to granis for this amazing port!
CS:GO Version is here: https://gamebanana.com/maps/208605

Hope you enjoy!
